Changelog
=========

0.1.0 - released July 7th, 2014
-------------------------------
Initial release.

unreleased
----------
- Added a CMSAttachMenu, which exposes Oscar's categories as CMS menu entries.

0.2.0 - released March 8, 2017
----------------------------------

- Refactored FeaturedProduct plugin, it's now compatible with Django-CMS 3.4.2
- Added ViewedProducts plugin, which replaces recently_viewed_products tag in the Django-CMS pages
- Added Russian locale and translation